data.text:
N album is the 15th original album by KinKi Kids. Released on September 21, 2016. The publisher is Johnny's Entertainment.

This is the first album in about 1 year and 9 months since the previous album. The theme of this album is "naked & natural," and it is an album that combines the "natural and natural" sensibilities of the two artists, who have been active both as KinKi Kids and as solo artists. Additionally, we are currently holding the "KinKi Kids 20th Anniversary Campaign", which will target products released by KinKi Kids by the end of the 20th anniversary year in 2017. When you collect points, you can receive benefits according to the number of points, and this work is also a campaign target work.
